# emotion-videos.eyetrackprep: a Courtois-NeuroMod subdataset 
## eye-tracking derivatives for the emotion-videos CNeuroMod dataset 

The [Courtois project on Neural Modelling (Courtois NeuroMod)](https://www.cneuromod.ca/) is assembling an extensive dataset of individual human brain activity, physiological and behavioural data.

The current sub-dataset contains drift-corrected gaze coordinates and metrics of pupil dilation to complement the BOLD response for the emotion-videos dataset.
